main_body:
Regulation (EEC) No 3976/87 is hereby amended as follows:
1.  in Article 2 (2) a new indent is added reading as follows:
'- consultations on cargo rates,';
2.  in Article 3, '31 January 1991' is replaced by '31 December 1992';
3.  in Article 8, '30 June 1990' and '1 November 1989' are replaced by '31 December 1992' and '1 July 1992' respectively.
